Show me one.

20
00:01:08,710 --> 00:01:09,830
Alright, alright.

21
00:01:10,560 --> 00:01:11,480
Come on.

22
00:01:11,750 --> 00:01:12,830
Look at me.

23
00:01:14,480 --> 00:01:15,870
You were like...

24
00:01:19,590 --> 00:01:21,120
This is how you look right now.

25
00:01:21,680 --> 00:01:22,760
A gentle expression.

26
00:01:30,040 --> 00:01:30,880
Have you learned it?

27
00:01:30,880 --> 00:01:31,790
Yes, we have.

28
00:01:31,800 --> 00:01:32,660
Good.

29
00:01:32,680 --> 00:01:33,600
Show me one. Come on.

30
00:01:39,560 --> 00:01:40,480
See?

31
00:01:40,680 --> 00:01:42,000
Isn't that much better?

32
00:01:42,920 --> 00:01:44,790
Good. Very good.

33
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:47,480
Young Master, you're a good teacher.

34
00:01:47,680 --> 00:01:48,720
Now listen carefully.

35
00:01:49,040 --> 00:01:50,510
Follow the Young Master's teachings.

36
00:01:50,760 --> 00:01:51,680
Practice it more.

37
00:01:51,680 --> 00:01:52,590
Did you hear me?

38
00:01:52,590 --> 00:01:53,510
Yes!

